GTVerificationInfo_st Struct Reference
[Verification]

This structure represents verification info of a timestamp.

Field Documentation

GTTimeStampExplicit* GTVerificationInfo_st::explicit_data

Explicit values extracted from the timestamp. Only present if parsing of the timestamp was requested in the call to GTTimestamp_verify().

GTTimeStampImplicit* GTVerificationInfo_st::implicit_data

Implicit values computed from the timestamp. Always present.

int GTVerificationInfo_st::verification_errors

Bitmap of errors found in the timestamp during verification. See GTVerificationError for meaning of the bits.

int GTVerificationInfo_st::verification_status

Bitmap of conditions discovered during verification. See GTVerificationStatus for meaning of the bits.

int GTVerificationInfo_st::version

Version of the VerificationInfo structure. Currently always 2.
